iaik.tc.tss.api.tspi
Interface TcIMigData

All Superinterfaces:
TcIAttributes, TcIWorkingObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
TcMigData
public interface TcIMigData
extends TcIWorkingObject, TcIAttributes

This class is used with Certified Migratable Keys (CMKs) to hold properties and migratable data blobs when passing them between APIs. This class just has attributes which can be set and retrieved using Tspi_SetAttribData() and Tspi_GetAttribData(). There are no further function defined for this class.
